    "title": "Wayahudi na Mataifa (Wasio Wayahudi)",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "wayahudi na mataifa (wasio wayahudi)",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mada kuu ya Agano Jipya ni kwamba Mungu amewajumuisha watu wasio Wayahudi (wanaoitwa Mataifa) katika watu wake huku akitimiza ahadi zake kwa Israeli. Katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:11-Rom11:32\">Warumi 11:11–32</a>, mtume Paulo anaeleza mpango wa Mungu wa kuokoa mataifa yote katika hatua nne zilizoelezwa wazi:</p><ol><li><p>Mitume wanashiriki habari njema kuhusu Yesu na Wayahudi, lakini wengi wao hawaamini.</p><p>Paulo anatumia mti wa mzeituni kama mfano. Anasema, “matawi mengine yamevunjika” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:17\">Warumi 11:17</a>). Hatua hii ilikuwa tayari imetokea na Paulo aliipitia mwenyewe. Alishiriki habari njema na Wayahudi katika maeneo yao ya ibada (masinagogi) katika eneo la mashariki ya Mediterania. Hata hivyo, Wayahudi wengi walikataa ujumbe wa Paulo (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:42-Acts13:49\">Matendo 13:42–49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:4-Acts18:6\">18:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:23-Acts28:28\">28:23–28</a>).</p></li><li><p>Watu wengi ambao si Wayahudi wanapokea ujumbe na kumwamini Yesu.</p><p>Baada ya Mungu kuondoa &quot;matawi ya asili,&quot; anachomeka &quot;chipukizi la mzeituni mwitu&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:17\">Warumi 11:17</a>). Paulo na mitume wengine walikumbana na upinzani katika masinagogi. Kwa hivyo, waliwahubiria wasio Wayahudi, na wengi walikubali habari njema (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:48-Acts13:49\">Matendo 13:48–49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:15-Acts26:18\">26:15–18</a>). Kufikia wakati Paulo aliandika barua kwa Warumi, kanisa katika Rumi lilikuwa jamii isiyo ya Kiyahudi kwa kiasi kikubwa.</p></li><li><p>Wayahudi wengi wanakubali Injili na kumwamini Yesu.</p><p>Kuhusu &quot;matawi ya asili,&quot; Mungu anaweza &quot;kuwapandikiza tena&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:23\">Warumi 11:23</a>). Paulo anasema kwamba Wayahudi hawako &quot;nje ya kupona&quot; na wanaweza kumgeukia Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:11\">11:11</a>). Paulo ana matumaini kwamba wakati wasio Wayahudi wanapokea baraka za wokovu, Wayahudi watahisi kutiwa moyo na kujibu habari njema (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:11\">11:11–15</a>).</p></li><li><p>Mungu anatoa baraka kubwa kwa ulimwengu, ikiwemo ufufuo wa wafu.</p><p>Paulo anapendekeza kwamba wakati Wayahudi wengi watakapomwamini Kristo, itabariki sana ulimwengu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:12\">Warumi 11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:15\">15</a>). Wale wanaokubali toleo la Mungu la wokovu, iwe ni Wayahudi au wasio Wayahudi, wanapata &quot;uzima kutoka kwa wafu&quot; (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:15\">11:15</a>). Siku moja wataona &quot;ufufuo wa wafu&quot; (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:20-1Cor15:26\">1 Wakorintho 15:20–26</a>). Mwishoni mwa historia, jamii kubwa ya Wayahudi na wasio Wayahudi watamsifu Mungu kwa rehema zake. Kisha kila mtu ataona na kuelewa hekima na upendo mkuu wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33-Rom11:36\">Warumi 11:33–36</a>).</p></li></ol><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7-Deut7:8\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 7:7–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:19-Deut32:21\">32:19–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:1-Isa9:3\">Isaya 9:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:6\">49:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:15-Matt4:16\">Mathayo 4:15–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:10-Matt8:12\">8:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:21-Matt15:28\">15:21–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:20-Luke21:24\">Luka 21:20–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38-Acts2:39\">Matendo 2:38–39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:45-Acts10:46\">10:45–46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:12-Acts11:18\">11:12–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:42-Acts13:49\">13:42–49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:4-Acts18:6\">18:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:15-Acts26:18\">26:15–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:23-Acts28:28\">28:23–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:5-Rom1:6\">Warumi 1:5–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16-Rom1:17\">16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:9-Rom2:10\">2:9–10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:24-Rom2:27\">24–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:9\">3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:29-Rom3:30\">29–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:25-Rom9:33\">9:25–33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:11-Rom10:13\">10:11–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:11-Rom11:36\">11:11–36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:7-Rom15:13\">15:7–13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:27\">27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1 Wakorintho 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:8-Gal2:21\">Wagalatia 2:8–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:8-Gal3:9\">3:8–9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:26-Gal3:29\">26–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:11-Eph2:22\">Waefeso 2:11–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:6\">3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:11\">Wakolosai 3:11</a></p>",
